core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af99d60628486fd2bbd72e0666de1fe76ccd0ee9","tid":1715824,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64641e7447faa3fe2e00368a60b3f9319e642d37","tid":1715824,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"講一億次係宣告中國毁約<br />\n唔係廢約<br />\n<br />\n最新英國下議院報告<br />\n先大大聲講聲明有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n We reiterate our view that the Sino- British Joint Declaration on Hong Kong is a legally binding international treaty registered at the United Nations. Its validity and implementation are of profound importance both to UK national interests and to the health of the rules-based international system. </span></span></strong>We are therefore deeply concerned by the events in Hong Kong over the last six months, which have demonstrated that Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy is at risk, especially in the area of the rule of law, which underpins its economy.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpF6gbq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpF6gbq.png&h=d81db0b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[url][url][url]<a href=\"https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201920/cmselect/cmfaff/109/109.pdf[/url[/url][/url]］[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.parliament.uk%2Fpa%2Fcm201920%2Fcmselect%2Fcmfaff%2F109%2F109.pdf%5B%2Furl%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D%EF%BC%BD%5B%2Fquote%5D&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=f7186de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201920/cmselect/cmfaff/109/109.pdf[/url[/url][/url]］[/quote]</a><br />\n<br />\n美國一樣講聲明（第三段後半部）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTuvhcU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTuvhcU.jpg&h=35903f6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c24f3132ceb0d322ea570d4a11431c619a63ec9","tid":1715824,"uid":56015,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"OP 又喺度開post mislead 人<br />\nOP 已經開咗好幾個posts 係咁mislead 人叫人支持英國廢除聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\n但明明基於英國國會主權原則, 所以係應該叫英國國會出bill 指出中國已經違反聯合聲明. 英國自己走去廢約的話, 錯就喺英國度. OP 不斷mislead 人咩居心?"},{"pid":"9376d63541fab615683f70d527fa783e2aa5d52a","tid":1715824,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"Eight-Nation Alliance this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cf0f37383ecc114c227b866ad6f683b00aaffc","tid":1715824,"uid":168359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"a3bcf6f3e7922dd12625c5b514b9a2c3b24880bc","tid":1715824,"uid":308618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"支持港共打英國領事館 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">到時我加入英軍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1fdb94dba456bab33cbdee2a178a7b8c82c95457","tid":1715824,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"c44f928e730658395853f9d62e16d24ab8b94dbb","tid":1715824,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-