sg":"係中國毁約喎 說好的高度自治都無撚左<br />\n仲唔係歸英國管? 雖然英國自己都好頭痕要脫歐<br />\n點解成日都提廢除聯合聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pCHU5V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pCHU5V.jpg&h=de94ac89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3yv3Zi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3yv3Zi.jpg&h=b00fb1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Ava3Zk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Ava3Zk.jpg&h=5106be4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJ4nU52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJ4nU52.jpg&h=3513a39d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFRtQEq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFRtQEq.jpg&h=7ac5e960&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vjmEXjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvjmEXjr.png&h=923b7b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢聲明就廢中国主權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"OP 又喺度開post mislead 人<br />\nOP 已經開咗好幾個posts 係咁mislead 人叫人支持英國廢除聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\n但明明基於英國國會主權原則, 所以係應該叫英國國會出bill 指出中國已經違反聯合聲明. 英國自己走去廢約的話, 錯就喺英國度. OP 不斷mislead 人咩居心?"},{"pid":"83e9577d3d3a9a2a96e0f58f62b044b4d2aa2707","tid":1715824,"uid":297453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"BNO人依家去英領有冇用？"},{"pid":"47ad467e2eabe02c911f5abed95031a9a098d180","tid":1715824,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"bcda4e4f2aeab1395ce5a1ed00e120b8603fe37d","tid":1715824,"uid":84267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uMPvjLS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMPvjLS.jpg&h=cef5ca16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立黨係分化撚黎"},{"pid":"553826605ab88f858986536f8d6460a9afa2573c","tid":1715824,"uid":84267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"睇到呢度<br />\n應該有人問點解會有幾條on9不停追擊樓主<br />\n<br />\n好簡單<br />\n因為樓主嘅政黨HKIP非常有問題<br />\n要利用中英聯合聲明, 正路首先係要求英國外交部正式宣佈中英聯合聲明被違反.<br />\n<br />\n但HKIP不停標榜英國要廢除中英聯合聲明<br />\n點解要用廢除一字? 根本唔合理<br />\n英國一日未正式宣佈中國違約, 英國係唔可以基於違約而做嘢<br />\n睇翻樓主個post, 無一句係要求英國正式宣佈中國違反聯合聲明. 但就首先要求英國直接&quot;廢除&quot;. <br />\n喺未有宣佈中國違約嘅條件下, 單方面直接廢除就係英國違約.<br />\n<br />\n但明明依家係中國違約而唔係英國違約<br />\n點解HKIP不停標榜英國要廢除中英聯合聲明?<br />\n再加上, 廢聯合聲明並不等於重新取回香港主權<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">廢除中英聯合聲明 唔等於 宣佈聲明失效<br />\n廢除中英聯合聲明 唔等於 恢復主權</span><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度, 明眼人都睇得出樓主嘅政黨HKIP係有莫大企圖<br />\n繼續撐HKIP嘅, 唔緊要, 但至少你搞清楚何謂&quot;廢除&quot;聯合聲明同會帶黎嘅後果<br />\n<br />\n更加唔使講HKIP以往嘅Poland Ball眾籌. 咁垃圾小學雞嘅野都想呃人錢去登報. 獨立黨有幾多斤兩自己諗<br />\n<br />\n仲要一次過話攬炒, gphone, IAD係共匪係鬼<br />\n獨立黨就係咁, 所有人都係做唔到野, 只有獨立黨先做到野<br />\n咁獨立黨做過咩實事? 一封回信<br />\n真係得咁多<br />\n<br />\n其他人沈默奮鬥, 就只有獨立黨先會咁大聲, 仲要無實事做過<br />\n自己諗<br />\n<br />\n所以呢度幾條on9計埋我不停追擊樓主, 係有原因"},{"pid":"9354e9d34a7c927ac768b4aed58680ce27d3cc0c","tid":1715824,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83e9577d3d3a9a2a96e0f58f62b044b4d2aa2707","tid":1715824,"uid":297453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"BNO人依家去英領有冇用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"有 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VchgZMO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVchgZMO.jpg&h=1fa939be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bac953f17e87049671b947957034caf89dbdd53","tid":1715824,"uid":258475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:39:44.000Z","msg":"唔係應該話中國<br />\n違反中英聯合聲明咩？"},{"pid":"921499ef49a95aed345172ab88cbf851d0a191bd","tid":1715824,"uid":56015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s